Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's chef's special entrée is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking that we haven't done this for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, eating dinner together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's very true, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to call me Papa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't come to this kind of place so often, so I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a funny girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's everything. Please take extra care during this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be awaiting good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will certainly bring good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika and Michikusa are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what are your plans for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to continue working as a Salvager?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has become a better place in recent days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for you to plan your future more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Salvager is one who searches for an inheritance from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People shouldn't do that kind of work forever, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should find something better...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any intention of quitting this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like being a Salvager!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue doing this job with you and Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Michikusa, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked for four hours on this and was just about to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.19,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The constellations that decorate the summer night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:59.11,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The diamonds start to twinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.87,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting go into the time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:11.25,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to warm the body, tired from swimming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:23.55,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended not to notice the smile that hides the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:30.56,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's an endless dream (keep on going)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:35.86,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:42.53,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your true self (it's up to you)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:47.87,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:56.25,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Look only at the irreplaceable future
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.43,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,322)}Decisive Break-in! Delmo Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, see you later. Be careful going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika should have skipped work and joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our office is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Rion, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what happened to the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see? It collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Delmos blew it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just surprised, because I came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I saw the office, and it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Delmos hit him with a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll take him four months to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Then, what about Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sad! You shouldn't be like this, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead now. We can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming back even if you cry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said she's dead?! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not dead! Aika wouldn't die this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Rion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the Delmo's hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find where it is, and break into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have revenge for Aika and Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Did you forget something, Rion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! That hurts, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! Oh, Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me this is a lie, Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how long are you going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really annoying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know. I understand you were serious about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But crying doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never understand that my sadness is deeper than the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika! My honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if your body is grown up, your mind is still like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't this happen to the old man instead of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have asked her out to dinner at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, walk by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I politely refuse to take revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rion! Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I just take this shit and do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you give me some help? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I poke my nose into another company's problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry about Aika, and your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my sympathies, but this and that are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if something bad were to happen to you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make your father worried or even more sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I said I'll do it, so I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can forgive the Delmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! You don't have to help me! I'll get revenge for Aika myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Papa will understand my feelings too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why don't you say something to her, Gusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I understand. I'll help you, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandra got angry and left. Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't matter at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who decided to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you guys can completely rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's find out the Delmo's hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Gusto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Gusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, managing intelligence data was all handled by Bandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how to do such things, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that? How can I rely on your empty brain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I know somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's very familiar with that kind of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be able to find the Delmo's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might even be able to give us help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me that she was a former A-class special secret agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former A-class special secret agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Meipia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, long time no see, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, you guys knew each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I get for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inuboe Island. People call it Lighthouse Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally get revenge for Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, couldn't you find a better ship than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! This kind of ship is less suspicious than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Michikusa, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hovercraft is approaching us, so I'm saying hello to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Delmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! One more from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you mean, this boat is less suspicious? Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to fight! They're surrounding us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew this might happen, so we were watching you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want all of you to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target is that pleasure boat about four hundred meters ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster! Faster! They're gaining on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are. Their ship is much faster than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive. Was I saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So was everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is perfect for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look cute this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michikusa, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Let's go everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're confirming that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is gonna be our avenging battle for Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destroy everything, Rion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders are now moving from F block to the third floor of E block.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Close gates number 5, 7, 8, and 16!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lure them into one area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! I'll seal gates number 5, 7, 8, and 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michikusa, what are you doing? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you guys were tricked by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, if it isn't you two, Miss Aika's appendix.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by appendix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's got us pegged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't agree with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you guys planning to take revenge for Aika Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those two your bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Come on and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, but I'm afraid that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponents this time are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are your opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Delmo Sania!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, Tonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think we're so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't even a threat anymore, with Aika Sumeragi gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! I'll call for help right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-haired woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering what they did, they have to pay dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why don't you kill us if you want to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. I have no intention of dying yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll kill everybody together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Aika must be waiting eagerly for everybody to join her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! But I'm not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, I knew you were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have made you worry, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Aika Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you disturbed us? But this time it ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I intend. Let's end this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. This was my favorite one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sania...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll abandon this base, and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, commander, if we lose the base, how do we...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hurt our comrades any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ordering to end the operation against Aika Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also prohibit any further contact with Aika Sumeragi from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! Are you sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will start over from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will settle this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention! We're abandoning this base!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel will evacuate this base immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone back to living in a trailer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing we can do about it. It's just that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our President seems to be recovering faster than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rion. If you're concerned about something, I will be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? It's about you! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my kappa doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of our situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ouch! Please don't do that! It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:25.98,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:30.11,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not above being cool for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.11,0:24:34.45,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, tell me what you want, what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:38.41,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hardest time, you still look so good to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.41,0:24:42.79,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can ease your mind, ease your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.79,0:24:46.71,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have your fears just like every man
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:50.55,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannot be sure of yourself all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.13,0:24:55.51,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just close your eyes, I'll turn the music on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:24:59.51,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna do what you got to do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.02,0:25:07.65,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight, 'cause I make you feel all right
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:11.57,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fell in love at sight? I don't want to make a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.53,0:25:15.70,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me tonight, if you wanna hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.70,0:25:18.87,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say maybe, come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.62,0:25:24.04,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,So dance with me tonight, 'cause I make you feel all right
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.79,0:25:28.21,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fell in love at sight? I don't want to make a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.92,0:25:32.46,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me tonight, if you wanna hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.46,0:25:35.51,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say maybe, come to me
